SHOP RESTOCK Alert!🚨 August 18th at 9pm EST is when it's happening!
💜
This purple beauty will be available along with over 70+ pretty pipes! 😻💕
💜
In other news I just got a review section in my shop up and running finally. 😅 Link in bio if you would like to share.💜💕💜
Infinite love and gratitude to you all for sticking with me on my journey as I navigate running a small art business. 💜
